  "narrative": "# Turn 45\n\n*7 commanders issued orders this turn.*\n\n## Strategic Decisions\n\n### CURATOR (artifact collector)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W22, W27.\n\n### NOMAD (merchant)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W22, W6.\n\n### PROPHET (apostle)\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 1 fleets; unloaded at 2 destinations; commissioned 8 new ships.\n\n### REAVER (pirate)\n\nDispatched 4 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W31, W24, W5, W10.\n\n### SOLARIS (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W30, W4.\n\nEconomic activity: invested in 2 units of industry.\n\n### TERRAN (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W20, W27.\n\nEconomic activity: invested in 6 units of industry.\n\n### TRADER (merchant)\n\nDispatched 3 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W17, W17, W6.\n\n## Consequences\n\n### Territorial Shifts\n\n- **TRADER** seized control of W17 (previously TERRAN).\n\n- **SOLARIS** seized control of W30 (previously TERRAN).\n\n### Fleet Movements\n\n- **CURATOR** moved: F8\u2192W22, F7\u2192W27\n\n- **NOMAD** moved: F15\u2192W22, F16\u2192W6\n\n- **REAVER** repositioned 4 fleets across the sector.\n\n- **SOLARIS** moved: F1\u2192W30, F2\u2192W4\n\n- **TERRAN** moved: F13\u2192W20, F14\u2192W27\n\n- **TRADER** moved: F4\u2192W17, F3\u2192W6\n\n### Production\n\n- **PROPHET** launched 8 new ships.\n\n- **SOLARIS** built 2 industry.\n\n- **TERRAN** built 6 industry.\n"
